## ⚙️ How these packs were made

Converted from [{{upstream_repo}}]({{upstream_link}}) with the OpenASR importer:

```bash
openasr model-pack {{import_subcommand}} <src> <out>.oasr \
  --package-id {{registry_id}} --quantization {fp16,q8-0,q4-k}
```

The `.oasr` container is GGUF-backed; packs use zero-copy mmap weight binding and graph
buffer reuse to keep peak memory low.

